# Davids Daily Blog My third idea is just a daily blog, i have been struggling with declining health and health issue the past few years. At 29 years old i feel i could offer some help in a way to others going thorugh similar things. I would share my day and how i cope with and manage my health issues.![Blog image](https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTMwlE0jyPB8vtww24MyOPtxi8GCt5LLlu4TQ&s)
